{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>The problem</h2>\n<p><strong>The option to customize a Correctbook is, at the moment, an obstructive process that takes a lot of steps and time which makes it unattractive for companies to purchase their customized Correctbooks.</strong></p>\n<p>In the current flow, companies can request a quotation on the Correctbook website. Next, Correctbook asks for a detailed design to be sent or, on request, makes a design if the company itself has little design experience. This flow is not ideal for both parties. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Requesting a quote is a threshold for customers, because it is unclear how this process works and what the possibilities are in the design</li>\n<li>The process takes a long time </li>\n<li>It takes Correctbook a lot of time to create designs at the customer's request, which limits the number of customers that can be served at the same time</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d8a96fb0e58bb1b59ccca0c690143ccf/216e4/customer-journey.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 80.03502626970229%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Customer journey\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d8a96fb0e58bb1b59ccca0c690143ccf/54cd2/customer-journey.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d8a96fb0e58bb1b59ccca0c690143ccf/850a0/customer-journey.jpg 150w,\n/static/d8a96fb0e58bb1b59ccca0c690143ccf/ff74a/customer-journey.jpg 300w,\n/static/d8a96fb0e58bb1b59ccca0c690143ccf/54cd2/customer-journey.jpg 600w,\n/static/d8a96fb0e58bb1b59ccca0c690143ccf/3f36a/customer-journey.jpg 900w,\n/static/d8a96fb0e58bb1b59ccca0c690143ccf/65430/customer-journey.jpg 1200w,\n/static/d8a96fb0e58bb1b59ccca0c690143ccf/2adc3/customer-journey.jpg 1800w,\n/static/d8a96fb0e58bb1b59ccca0c690143ccf/216e4/customer-journey.jpg 2284w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>The challenge</h2>\n<p><strong>Create a designtool, accessible to companies with and without design experience, so that all companies can design and order their own Correctbooks.</strong></p>\n<p>Not all customers of Correctbook have the ability or skills to make their own design. Therefore, the designtool should focus on different types of users with varying designexperience.</p>\n<p>Because more than half the visitors of correctbook.com visit the site by using their mobile device, Correctbook asked us to design a mobile-first design tool. </p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Method</h2>\n<p><strong>To find out what the tool should or should not contain, we conducted five interviews and tested comparable services (e.g. Hema, Fotofabriek, Greetz etc.) with the interviewees.</strong></p>\n<p>Because there is already a big market in customizing products, we choose to conduct competitive research and test these services with the interviewees. During the test the the interviewees were asked to personalize a Hema notebook or Greetz card and to think out loud while performing their tasks. Through observation of their behaviour, asking what, how, which, why questions and making notes, we got the first early insights.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c39acf40c4cebb3ac16226f139b9e3fb/2ce16/method-image.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 93.97590361445783%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Method\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c39acf40c4cebb3ac16226f139b9e3fb/54cd2/method-image.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c39acf40c4cebb3ac16226f139b9e3fb/850a0/method-image.jpg 150w,\n/static/c39acf40c4cebb3ac16226f139b9e3fb/ff74a/method-image.jpg 300w,\n/static/c39acf40c4cebb3ac16226f139b9e3fb/54cd2/method-image.jpg 600w,\n/static/c39acf40c4cebb3ac16226f139b9e3fb/3f36a/method-image.jpg 900w,\n/static/c39acf40c4cebb3ac16226f139b9e3fb/65430/method-image.jpg 1200w,\n/static/c39acf40c4cebb3ac16226f139b9e3fb/2ce16/method-image.jpg 1328w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Understand the user</h2>\n<p><strong>The user tests showed that users had different needs for guidance during the design of their own correctbook. They also needed a constant overview of the design options and direct feedback of changes to the design.</strong></p>\n<p>Because the need for design guidance among the customers varied, we collected and analyzed the data to define persona’s and their goals and painpoints. This resulted in two persona’s: Nikki and Harry. These two were opposite to each other in terms of design skills and pain points. </p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2eb889dc34e34d95a6ebb234c7da0ac4/a2e00/images-persona.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 153.25443786982248%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Personas\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2eb889dc34e34d95a6ebb234c7da0ac4/54cd2/images-persona.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2eb889dc34e34d95a6ebb234c7da0ac4/850a0/images-persona.jpg 150w,\n/static/2eb889dc34e34d95a6ebb234c7da0ac4/ff74a/images-persona.jpg 300w,\n/static/2eb889dc34e34d95a6ebb234c7da0ac4/54cd2/images-persona.jpg 600w,\n/static/2eb889dc34e34d95a6ebb234c7da0ac4/a2e00/images-persona.jpg 676w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>Users also reported a need for overview and direct feedback. Customizing a product on a website where you could design step by step by scrolling and indicating your preferences, was very unclear to users. They forgot what they had chosen or changed and could not see the result untill the end.</p>\n<p>Finally, users wanted to try out the design options as quickly as possible in the tool. There were often too many steps (number, size, interior) before they could start designing.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Prototyping and testing</h2>\n<p><strong>Based on the results of the test and the paintpoints in the current userflow, we made sketches and wireframes of the tool. We choose to show designoptions and direct feedback on one page, the give users the possibility to choose guidance, and to minimalize the steps before entering the designtool.</strong></p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/77d054d586b8ab603e987c415cd3ab24/a19f9/wireframe.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 95.44117647058823%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Wireframe\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/77d054d586b8ab603e987c415cd3ab24/54cd2/wireframe.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/77d054d586b8ab603e987c415cd3ab24/850a0/wireframe.jpg 150w,\n/static/77d054d586b8ab603e987c415cd3ab24/ff74a/wireframe.jpg 300w,\n/static/77d054d586b8ab603e987c415cd3ab24/54cd2/wireframe.jpg 600w,\n/static/77d054d586b8ab603e987c415cd3ab24/3f36a/wireframe.jpg 900w,\n/static/77d054d586b8ab603e987c415cd3ab24/65430/wireframe.jpg 1200w,\n/static/77d054d586b8ab603e987c415cd3ab24/a19f9/wireframe.jpg 1360w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>After multiple tests, iterations and refinement, we made a final design. Because the tool was designed for customers, we opted for a clean and minimal design using the colours and font matching the house-style of Correctbook.</p>\n<h4>Overview and feedback</h4>\n<p>Users wanted to make changes immediately and wanted direct feedback. We solved this by constantly showing the cover that the user is designing on one page while making it interactive. Text, photos, background color or templates can be added via a bar at the bottom of the screen. When a part is changed, the bar only shows the options to further modify the selected part.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"September 01, 2018","path":"/projects/correctbook","title":"Creating a designtool that inspires companies to customize their endlessly reusable notebook","supertitle":"Correctbook","image":{"childImageSharp":{"sizes":{"aspectRatio":1.57,"src":"/static/71c8d2282bc271defd630b83e996ab04/a9eb0/correctbook.jpg","srcSet":"/static/71c8d2282bc271defd630b83e996ab04/12a67/correctbook.jpg 150w,\n/static/71c8d2282bc271defd630b83e996ab04/c738d/correctbook.jpg 300w,\n/static/71c8d2282bc271defd630b83e996ab04/a9eb0/correctbook.jpg 600w,\n/static/71c8d2282bc271defd630b83e996ab04/c378d/correctbook.jpg 900w,\n/static/71c8d2282bc271defd630b83e996ab04/7d23f/correctbook.jpg 1200w,\n/static/71c8d2282bc271defd630b83e996ab04/a6adc/correctbook.jpg 1800w,\n/static/71c8d2282bc271defd630b83e996ab04/dfba7/correctbook.jpg 1884w","sizes":"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{}}